title: NFL Week 4 Fantasy/DFS Advice, Breakdown (Football 9/26)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings and Bryant McFadden for fantasy advice ahead of Week 4 in the NFL. The guys discuss the impact of Saquon Barkley's injury, running backs to target, BMac's lineups and some schedules to keep an eye on. Then, Will and Heath go over top plays for DFS this week.
